Package net.apartium.cocoabeans.structs

Record Class MinecraftVersion

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
net.apartium.cocoabeans.structs.MinecraftVersion
Record Components:
major - major version, currently only 1
update - , update version
minor - minor version, if not explicitly specified defaults to 0
protocol - protocol version
public record MinecraftVersion(int major, int update, int minor, int protocol) extends Record
Represents version in the game. Format: major.update.minor, ex 1.8.3
